itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Jarred Taylor, and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest Alex Jones from Info Wars for our election prediction show as we break down each state and Ross gives his exact Electoral College count.  Asking Alexandria lead singer Danny Worsnop stops by at the end to give his prediction on his home state of Florida.  This is one of the wildest episodes of all time.
